, \"to\": 1681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her husband, Michael, 59, who also spoke to the newspaper, said: \\\"I have never known anyone who is as mentally tough as her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her husband\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"Michael\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the newspaper\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[She] likes to run, likes to compete and it's a lifestyle for both of us.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lifestyle\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes her happy and I am just happy to be along for the ride,\\\" Michael said.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ride\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"Michael\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later adding, \\\"I told her, 'You have to do this because you might inspire some other people to keep going.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some other people\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like who does this?\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The answer is, no one else has.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The answer\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So just go do it and have fun doing it because you can.\\\"\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rohl trains every day and walks 45 miles a week at an 8-minute-a-mile pace, the outlet reported.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trains\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"an 8-minute-a-mile pace\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"the outlet\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris would have been her fourth time competing in the sporting event.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999115079884, \"rank\": 8.849203365482755e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fourth time\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting event\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She holds multiple individual age-group running records from 800 to 10,000 meters, the outlet reported.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple individual age-group running records\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"800 to 10,000 meters\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"the outlet\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, she set the American mile record for women in the 55 to 59 age group.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999893372273507, \"rank\": 7.24658560571595e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"the 55 to 59 age group\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rohl continued practicing the sport through numerous hurdles.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the s